# Frontend Rules (Next.js)

## Route Zones

| Zone | Path | Actor |
|------|------|-------|
| Seller | `app/(seller)/admin/` | Staff |
| Customer | `app/(customer)/my/` | GlobalCustomer |
| Marketing | `app/(marketing)/` | Public |

## Stack

- TanStack Query — server state
- React Hook Form + Zod — forms (schemas from `packages/contracts`)
- shadcn/ui + Tailwind — RTL-first, fa-IR primary

## Forms & Pages

Read `EXCELLENCE-STANDARDS.md` §5–7 before any form or page — all states required

## Rules

```typescript
// ✅ fetch via typed API client + TanStack Query
// ❌ amount calculation in JSX
// ❌ permission check only in UI — backend always enforces
// ❌ duplicate Zod schema — import from packages/contracts
```

## UI Permission

Hide menu/button if no permission — **but** this is UX only, not security

## Money Display

```typescript
// API returns amountRial as string/bigint
const toman = BigInt(amountRial) / 10n;
// Use locale formatter from packages/i18n
```

## Jalali

All user-facing dates: Jalali + Tehran timezone  
Use shared formatter — not ad-hoc in each page

## PWA (Customer)

- mobile-first for `(customer)/my/*`
- desktop-first acceptable for `(seller)/admin/*`

